Thanks for being my friend.  You have allowed me to take a boyish trip back in time.  I guess we were boys then...maybe boys now.  I still feel twenty years old in spite of wounds and injuries and 55 years of shelf life.<br>
I believe the grab ass was a good trip.  May have offended some by exclusion.  I always hoped everyone would have jumped in, but they didn't.<br>
Isolation is a pretty safe place to be.  Denial is a fair way of handling bad stuff.<br>
Like Cookie said... laughter and pain are really the same.. or something like that.<br>
God, in his infinite wisdom created continumms... you can't have hot without cold... wet without dry... and you can't have heros without cowards.  I guess Spatz does serve a purpose.<br><br>
Just threw my watch out the window...gained ten knots airspeed.<br><br>
A True Brother<br><br>
Tatekohomni Wambli
